---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import MarketGrowthChartApex from "../components/qdaria-business-plan/charts/MarketGrowthChartApex.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Market Growth Chart Test">
  <div class="container mx-auto py-8 px-4">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Global Quantum Computing Market Growth Projection (2020-2035)</h1>
    
    <div class="bg-slate-800 rounded-lg p-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <MarketGrowthChartApex
        id="market-growth-test"
        showDataTable={true}
        showControls={true}
        height="500px"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Enhanced Chart Features</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Scale toggle between logarithmic and linear representation</li>
        <li>Improved y-axis labeling with more intermediate values</li>
        <li>Enhanced data table with year-over-year growth rates</li>
        <li>CAGR (Compound Annual Growth Rate) calculation for each scenario</li>
        <li>Prominent $1 Trillion milestone annotation</li>
        <li>Tooltips include growth rate information</li>
        <li>More detailed grid lines for better readability</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 mt-8">Visualization Guide</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        This chart visualizes the projected economic impact of quantum computing from 2020 to 2035
        across three scenarios:
      </p>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-6">
        <div class="bg-slate-800 p-4 rounded-lg border border-blue-500">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-blue-500 mb-2">Base Case</h3>
          <p>The expected market growth trajectory with mainstream adoption of quantum computing technologies.</p>
          <p class="mt-2"><span class="font-bold">Milestone:</span> $1 Trillion by 2035</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-slate-800 p-4 rounded-lg border border-purple-500">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-purple-500 mb-2">Conservative Case</h3>
          <p>Slower adoption curve with more technical challenges to overcome.</p>
          <p class="mt-2"><span class="font-bold">Milestone:</span> $850 Billion by 2035</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-slate-800 p-4 rounded-lg border border-yellow-500">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-yellow-500 mb-2">Optimistic Case</h3>
          <p>Faster adoption and breakthrough applications driving rapid market expansion.</p>
          <p class="mt-2"><span class="font-bold">Milestone:</span> $1.3 Trillion by 2035</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-8 p-4 bg-slate-800 rounded-lg border border-green-500">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-green-500 mb-2">Viewing Tip</h3>
        <p>
          The logarithmic scale is ideal for visualizing exponential growth as it shows percentage changes 
          consistently. Switch to linear scale to see absolute value differences more clearly.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Additional styles for the test page */
  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
  }
  
  h1, h2, h3 {
    color: #ffffff;
  }
  
  p {
    color: #e2e8f0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  li {
    color: #e2e8f0;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
</style>
